                content += "<p>3. &nbsp;&nbsp; We believe in God the creator of the universe and humans, as written in the Book of Genesis (Genesis 1 and 2; John 1:1-3; Colossians 1:16; Romans 4:17; Romans 1:19-20).<p>";
