                content += "<p>13. &nbsp;&nbsp; We believe in the Lord Jesus Christ as the Bridegroom, King of kings and Lord of lords, who will come to judge the world with justice, and will reign in the Thousand Year Kingdom of Peace with the Bride, which is His Church. (Acts 1:11; Revelation 22:7; I Corinthians 15:24–25; I Thessalonians 4:16–17; II Thessalonians 1:7-9; Revelation 20:10–15; Revelation 19:11-16 ; I Timothy 6:15).</p>";
                content += "<p>14. &nbsp;&nbsp; We believe in the resurrection of the saints before the Millennial Kingdom of Peace and the resurrection of sinners after the Kingdom; saints will receive eternal life, sinners will appear before the throne of God to receive eternal judgment in the lake of fire. (Revelation 20:1–15; I Thessalonians 4:16–17).</p>";
                content += "<p>15. &nbsp;&nbsp; We believe in a new heaven and a new earth that contains the Truth, the eternal abode of Christ's blood redeemed people (I Peter I:18-19; II Peter 3:13; Revelation 21:1–18).</p>";
                content += "<p>16. &nbsp;&nbsp; We believe that worship meetings must be held regularly with solemnity and joy. (Acts 2:25; Exodus 23:25; Hebrews 10:25; Psalm 47:2; 100:1-5; 134:2; 150:1-5).</p>";
                content += "<p>17. &nbsp;&nbsp; We believe every government is God's appointed servant of God. (Romans 13:4; I Peter 2:17; I Timothy 2:1-2; Proverbs 21:1).</p>";

            }else{
